    believe that the manufacturers, affiliates, and other third parties whose products we promote or sell typically will
    respect your privacy; however, we don’t control what they do with data they receive from us. We therefore recommend
    that you check the privacy policy of any third-party manufacturer or affiliate whose products you choose to buy from
